THE RED, WHITE & BLUE STORY
A him is one or the most pooular and talented
trumpet players of our time. Because of the many demands
for his personal appearance he is a frequent air traveler,
and United is his favorite airline.
When United recently introduced its Red, White & Blue
transcontinental service, Al was among the first to try it.
As with almost every other person who has traveled
Red, White & Blue, he liked it
In fact. Al was so pleased with the new service that
United asked him to set his enthusiasm to music. He readily
agreed, and the result is his own composition, "Red, Whit &
Blue." It's a happy and pleasant tune. We like it, Al like it,
and we believe vou will like It 100.
